---
title: Honey Garlic-Glazed Barramundi with Buttery Soy-Ginger Veggies
description: A sweet, sticky honey garlic glaze and a hot broiler are all you need to transform barramundi into crispy deliciousness! Pair with a pile of soy-ginger sautéed peppers and cabbage for a quick, balanced meal the whole family will enjoy!
